        <h2>Available endpoints:</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><code>/api/status</code> - Get server status (GET)</li>
            <li><code>/api/echo</code> - Echo back JSON data (POST)</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="https-info">
            <h3>HTTPS Information</h3>
            <p>This server supports HTTPS connections. In development, it uses a self-signed certificate.</p>
